data.description:
New Listing! You will love this speculator 2-story pool home! This 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath home has a 2-car garage, giving you 2605 living  sq. ft. New flooring throughout, with a modern kitchen. Both bathrooms have been beautifully updated. A grand entryway into formal living space with French doors.  All of this situated on a oversized corner lot with a  tranquil lake view. TWO termite bonds are  transferable to new homeowner, AC is newer.
Close to the beach, shopping and I-95! Family friendly Suntree neighborhood with outstanding A rated schools!
